@startuml
title SQL injection - conceptual flow

actor Attacker
participant "Web Application" as W
database "Database" as DB

Attacker -> W: Submit malicious input in form field
W -> DB: Build unsafe query using input
DB --> W: Return unintended data
W --> Attacker: Expose sensitive information

note over W
Problem: input is not sanitized
and parameterized queries are not used
end note

@enduml